{
  "info": {
    "name": "Xentari Microservices",
    "description": "Xentari Event-Driven E-Commerce Microservice System\n\n## Architecture\n- **API Gateway**: http://localhost:8080 (single entry point)\n- **Eureka Dashboard**: http://localhost:8761\n- **RabbitMQ Management**: http://localhost:15672 (guest/guest)\n- **Swagger UI (Aggregated)**: http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html\n\n## Event Flow\n1. POST /api/orders → Order Created (PENDING)\n2. Inventory Service reserves stock → Stock Reserved\n3. Payment Service processes → Payment Completed\n4. Order Service confirms → Order Confirmed (CONFIRMED)\n5. Notification Service sends confirmation",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8080",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "productServiceUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8081",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "orderServiceUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8082",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "inventoryServiceUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8083",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "paymentServiceUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8084",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
